content: संचरः {@--1@} Passage, transit from one zodiacal sign to another. {@--2@} A way, path; यत्रौषधिप्र काशेन नक्तं दर्शितसंचराः <ls>Ku. 6. 43</ls>; <ls>R. 16. 12</ls> {@--3@} A narrow road, defile, difficult passage. {@--4@} Entrance, gate. {@--5@} The body. {@--6@} Killing. {@--7@} Development.
